---
title: Savoury Parmesan, Chive & Bacon Pancakes with Fennel & Rocket Salad | Serves 2
description: Craving pancakes but still want that savoury hit? We've got you covered with these cheesy bacon and chive pancakes drizzled
with herby mayo. Serve up with a side salad of fennel and rocket. We think there is no better way to start the day!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/savoury-bacon-parmesan-chive-pancakes-0e24a051.jpg
